    "Modernist art historian, pioneer African arts scholar and director, Museum of Primitive Art, 1957-63.": [],
    "Goldwater was the son of Sigismund S. Goldwater (1873-1942), an M.D.": [],
    "and visionary commissioner of Hospitals in New York under Mayor La Guardia.": [
