    "The following year a revised version of his thesis appeared as the book with the nearly imperceptible title change, <em>Primitivism in Modern Painting</em>.": [],
    "The work became a landmark text in charting the relationship between tribal arts and twentieth-century painting.": [],
    "That year, too, he married a French student of Ferdinand Leger, the artist Louise Bourgeois (1911-2010) in Paris.": [],
    "In 1939 he accepted an appointment at Queens College, Brooklyn, NY, teaching art history there until 1956.": [
