    "Goldwater became editor of <em>The Magazine Art</em> in 1948, accepting the first articles on Abstract Expressionists in the journal.": [],
    "In 1949 he co-curated a show at the Museum of Modern art with Director <a href=\"/dharnoncourtr\">Ren\u00e9 d'Harnoncourt</a> entitled <em>Modern Art in Your Life</em>.": [
        [
