    "A separate library at the Metropolitan Museum, containing the Primitive Museum's holdings, was established as the Robert Goldwater Library in his memory.": [],
    "The Michael Rockefeller wing was opened in 1982.": [],
    "Goldwater's wife, Louise Bourgeois, became an important 20th-century surrealist and feminist sculptor.": [],
